subject: Re: New QuikScript font: QuikScript Geometric
msgSnippet: Hey guys, I m 5hwb, the creator of Quikscript Geometric. Glad to see that other people like it! I made my font using Inkscape to draw the glyphs and Fontforge
messageBody: Hey guys, I'm 5hwb, the creator of Quikscript Geometric. Glad to see that other people like it! I made my font using Inkscape to draw the glyphs and Fontforge to create the final font.
